:: Mansion Enter
<<set $location to "avery_mansion">><<set $bus to "avery_garden">><<set $outside to 1>><<effects>><<avery_mansion>>
<<set $avery_passage to "Mansion Garden">>
<<avery_mansion_interrupt true>>
You walk up the hill towards Avery's mansion. The gates rattle open as you approach, allowing you entry.
<br><br>

<<if _avery_interrupt is "injury">>
	<<npc Avery>><<person1>>
	You hear glass shattering in the garage. Someone is in there.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Mansion Return Broken Bed]]>><</link>>
	<br>

<<elseif _avery_interrupt is "work">>
	<<npc Avery>><<person1>>

	Avery walks outside, <<his>> eyes locked on yours.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Mansion Return Bed Work]]>><</link>>
	<br>

<<elseif _avery_interrupt is "party_missed">>
	<<npc Avery>><<person1>>
	Avery walks outside, <<his>> eyes locked on yours.
	<br><br>
	<<link [[Next|Mansion Return Bed Assess]]>><</link>>
	<br>
<<elseif _avery_interrupt is "valentines_missed">>
	<<npc Avery>><<person1>>
	Avery walks outside, <<his>> eyes locked on yours.
	<br><br>
	<<link [[Next|Avery Valentines Missed Intro]]>><<unset $avery_valentines_missed>><<set $avery_valentines.missed_approach to true>><</link>>
	<br>
<<elseif _avery_interrupt is "valentines_ready">>
	<<set $avery_valentines.ready to true>>
	<<npc Avery>><<person1>>
	Avery walks outside and approaches you. <<Hes>> wearing <<his>> best, along with a smile. "I'm ready when you are," <<he>> says. "For the <span class="gold">Valentine's</span> date. I'll be waiting in the garage."
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Mansion Garage]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
	<br>
<<elseif _avery_interrupt is "valentines_approach">>

	<<npc "Avery">><<person1>>
	Avery walks outside, <<his>> eyes locked on yours, and a smile on <<his>> lips.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Avery Valentines Invite Mansion]]>><</link>>
	<br>

<<elseif _avery_interrupt is "date_ready">>
	<<set $avery_mansion.date_ready to true>>
	<<npc Avery>><<person1>>
	Someone walks outside and approaches you. It's Avery, wearing <<his>> best. "I'm ready when you are," <<he>> says. "For the date. I'll be waiting in the garage."
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Mansion Garage]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
	<br>

<<elseif _avery_interrupt is "party_prepare">>
	<<npc Avery>><<person1>>
	Avery walks outside, <<his>> eyes locked on yours.
	<br><br>
	<<link [[Next|Mansion Return Bed Party Prepare]]>><</link>>
	<br>

<<elseif _avery_interrupt is "party">>
	<<npc Avery>><<person1>>
	Avery walks outside, <<his>> eyes locked on yours.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Mansion Return Bed Party]]>><</link>>
	<br>

<<elseif _avery_interrupt is "skyscraper_approach">>
	<<set $avery_tower.stage to 3>>
	<<npc Avery>><<person1>>
	<<set $avery_tower.stage to 3>>
	Avery walks outside, <<his>> eyes locked on yours.
	<br><br>
	"I've just had the call," Avery says. <<Hes>> smiling. <span class="gold">"My skyscraper is finished at last."</span>
	<br><br>
	<<skyscraper_time>>

	<<if _skyscraper_time is "now">>
		"The blood moon is high, and the time is nigh," <<he>> rhymes.
		<<if $worn.upper.type.includes("formal") and $worn.lower.type.includes("formal")>>
			<<He>> examines your outfit, and smiles. "Good," <<he>> says, linking <<his>> arm with yours. "Come. Remy and Harper will be meeting us here. We journey to the skyscraper together."
			<br><br>
			<<link [[Go with Avery|Mansion Skyscraper Formal]]>><</link>>
			<br>
			<<link [[Visit the wardrobe first|Mansion Skyscraper Dress]]>><<pass 5>><</link>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<He>> examines your outfit. "Remy and Harper will soon be here. We journey to the skyscraper together." <<He>> grasps your hand. "Come on. I'll dress you myself."
			<br><br>
			<<link [[Go with Avery (0:05)|Mansion Skyscraper Dress]]>><<pass 5>><</link>>
			<br>
			<<link [[Refuse|Mansion Skyscraper Dress Refuse]]>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<if _skyscraper_time is "tonight">>
			"<span class="gold">The opening ceremony is tonight.</span> When the moon is blood red.
		<<elseif _skyscraper_time is "tomorrow">>
			"<span class="gold">The opening ceremony will be tomorrow.</span> When the moon is blood red.
		<<else>>
			"<span class="gold">The opening ceremony will be on the last day of the month.</span> When the moon is blood red.
		<</if>>
		They're inducting me into their circle, and it's vital you attend. There can be no ceremony without you."
		<br><br>
		Avery walks way, more animated than you've yet seen <<him>>. "Meet me here when the time comes. We'll arrive there in style."
		<br><br>

		<<link [[Next|Mansion Garden]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<<elseif _avery_interrupt is "skyscraper_ready">>
	<<npc "Avery">><<person1>>
	<<if $worn.upper.type.includes("formal") and $worn.lower.type.includes("formal")>>
		Avery examines your outfit, and smiles. "Good," <<he>> says, linking <<his>> arm with yours. "Come. Remy and Harper will be meeting us here. We journey to the skyscraper together."
		<br><br>
		<<link [[Go with Avery|Mansion Skyscraper Formal]]>><</link>>
		<br>
		<<link [[Visit the wardrobe first|Mansion Skyscraper Dress]]>><<pass 5>><</link>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		Avery examines your outfit. "The guests are arriving." <<He>> grasps your hand. "Come on. I'll dress you myself."
		<br><br>
		<<link [[Go with Avery (0:05)|Mansion Skyscraper Dress]]>><<pass 5>><</link>>
		<br>
		<<link [[Refuse|Mansion Skyscraper Dress Refuse]]>><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<link [[Next|Mansion Garden]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Mansion Pool
<<set $location to "avery_mansion">><<set $bus to "avery_pool">><<set $avery_passage to $passage>><<set $outside to 1>><<effects>><<avery_mansion>>

<<avery_mansion_contents>>

:: Mansion Garden
<<set $location to "avery_mansion">><<set $bus to "avery_garden">><<set $avery_passage to $passage>><<set $outside to 1>><<effects>><<getTarget true>><<avery_mansion>>

<<avery_mansion_contents>>

