:: Mansion Study Learn
<<effects>>

You scour Avery's library for recipe books. It takes a while, but you're able to find one. The ink is splotched and illegible throughout, except the page on <<recipe_name $phase "article">>.
<br><br>

<<if $housekeeping gte $plants[$phase].difficulty * 200>>
	<span class="red">It's too difficult.</span> You'd need to be more skilled at housekeeping to understand it.
	<br><br>
<<else>>
	The presentation is archaic, but you're able to follow. You could create this recipe, given the ingredients.
	<br><br>
	<<learn_recipe $phase>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if $avery_mansion.recipe.includes($phase)>>
	<<set $avery_mansion.recipe.delete($phase)>>
<</if>>

<<link [[Next|Mansion Study]]>><</link>>
<br>


