	<<else>>
		<<say_brown_fox "cap">> emerges.
	<</if>>
	"When the hand nears midnight, the world will tremble."
	Mickey swats <<his>> hand away. "Your approach is up to you. You're the field agents. The ones in the thick of it. I'll keep doing what I can." Mickey glances over their shoulder. "Good luck." They turn and leave, weaving between the trees.
	<br><br>

	<<say_brown_fox "cap">> only lingers for a moment. "You'll hear from me soon. I may have a lead, thanks to the little one." <<He>> folds <<his>> hands in front of <<himself>> and bows, before following Mickey.
	<<set $avery_mansion.mickey to 1>><<set $avery_mansion.fox.progress++>>
