:: Mansion Brown Fox Interrupt
<<effects>><<summon_brown_fox 1>><<person1>>
"Ever restless."
<br><br>

A <<personsimple>>'s voice makes you jump. You look towards the direction it came from, and see a figure in a hooded green cloak leaning against a tree.
<<He>> turns, revealing that <<hes>> wearing a brown fox mask. <span class="blue">The same one you saw speaking with Landry.</span>
<br><br>

"Have you had any luck finding the clutching bones? Or wishing stones, if you prefer?" <<His>> voice is gentle and soothing like birdsong. You snap out of it, and shake your head. <<He>> smiles patiently.
"Nor have I. They'll be hidden deep, deep down. Near the bottom, perhaps. They're Avery's lifeline to a life <<nnpc_he "Avery">> believes will make <<nnpc_him "Avery">> whole."
<<He>> shakes <<his>> head. "It will only leave larger <span class="purple">holes</span>. In <<nnpc_him "Avery">>, and the world."
