<<else>>
	"We'll see if Landry's trust was placed well."
<</if>>
<<He>> smiles warmly.
<<if $phase isnot 1>>
	"Ah! I usually work alone, so I've forgotten my manners. <span class="green">I'm the brown fox.</span>" <<He>> reaches forward, lifts your hand, and shakes it in both <<his>> own.
	"Because I jump over the lazy hounds. I already know you, though. <span class="teal"><<overworld_nickname "cap">></span> to the layperson, or <span class="pink"><<underworld_nickname "cap">></span> to those underneath. It's hard not to know about someone so interesting.
	If you need me, <span class="blue">ask for me from our mutual friend</span>. I'd like to know who Avery's next guest of honour is."
<<else>>
	"Ah! I usually work alone, so I've forgotten my manners." <<He>> reaches forward, lifts your hand, and shakes it in both <<his>> own. "It was a pleasure to meet you, even though we aren't really strangers.
	If you need me, <span class="blue">ask for me from our mutual friend</span>. I'd like to know who Avery's next guest of honour is."
<</if>>
