:: Mansion Brown Fox Wounded Ask Remy
<<effects>>
<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
	"How in the world did you get away from Remy?"
<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
	"How did you escape Remy? Not as fast off a horse?"
<<else>>
	"How did you get away from Remy?"
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<Hes>> quiet for a moment.
<br><br>

"<<nnpc_He "Remy">> caught me, and wasn't gentle. <<nnpc_He "Remy">> really didn't want me getting away." <<He>> frowns.
<<if $avery_mansion.fox.remy_warn>>
	"I was a little more prepared for <<nnpc_him "Remy">> thanks to you, though. I knew I was burnt already, so I didn't have to hesitate.
<<else>>
	"I hesitated. I thought I could slip back into the party." <<He>> shakes <<his>> head. "It was a mistake, and it took me too long to start fighting back.
<</if>>
I bit <<nnpc_him "Remy">>. A lot. Once I squirmed free, I started throwing anything I could find at <<nnpc_him "Remy">> as we ran. A few glass bottles, rocks, I think there was a brick at some point?"
<br><br>

<<link [[Help <<him>> walk to safety|Mansion Brown Fox Wounded 2]]>><<famegood 20>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[Tell <<him>> you don't need <<his>> help|Mansion Brown Fox Wounded 2]]>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
<br>

:: Mansion Brown Fox Wounded 2
<<effects>>
<<if $phase is 1>>
	<<if $physique gte 11000>>
		You go to lift <<him>> up by the arm, and realise that <<hes>> not very heavy. You put your other arm under <<his>> legs and lift <<him>> up completely. <<He>> yelps in surprise, and wraps <<his>> arms around you.
	<<else>>
		You lift <<him>> up by the arm, and put it over your shoulder. <<He>> yelps in surprise as you make <<him>> stand up all the way up.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<He>> looks away from you, <<his>> face still very red. <<if $brownFoxRevealed>><<gyearning>><<else>><<note "+ ???" "forest-green">><</if>>
	<<set $avery_mansion.fox.progress += 2>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen>>
		<<npcincr Gwylan dom 2>>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("bf_aid")>>
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	You walk <<him>> down the boulevard, keeping out of sight. "You're taking a big risk helping me, you know."
	<br><br>

	<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
		"And what about you? You're hurt because of a risk you took helping me. Shush and save your energy," you say.
	<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
		"Oh, shut up already. You already helped me, we're just even now," you say.
	<<else>>
		"I know, and you're taking an even bigger risk with what you're doing to help me," you say.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<He>> smiles at that.
<<else>>
	<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
		"I'll be alright. You should take care of yourself first, that looks really bad."
	<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
		"I won't need your help anyways. Get yourself checked out or something, and don't bleed on the grass."
	<<else>>
		"I don't need your help. You should take care of yourself first."
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<He>> looks down, as if ashamed.
<</if>>
"You'll be on your own from here on." <<He>> pauses. "Well. There may be a way I can still help, if you don't want to play Avery's game. I won't be able to sneak in for a while, but there's more subtle things we can do.
<span class="blue">If you want to work together on this, go to Landry and ask for me the next time you know who your party guests will be.</span>"
<br><br>

<<He>> places a hand on <<his>> chest, and the other on your forehead. "You tread a dangerous path. I wish you all the fortune of the sky, land, and sea."
<<if $phase is 1>>
	You reach the main streets, <<if $physique gte 11000>>and you put <<him>> down<<else>>and <<he>> starts to walk on <<his>> own<</if>>. <<He>> smiles at you brightly, before turning and hobbling to the east. "I hope to see you again."
<<else>>
	<<He>> starts to hobble down Danube Boulevard. "I hope to see you again."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<set $brownFoxWounded to true>>

<<link [[Next|Danube Street]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
<br>

