<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
	"I trust there's a reason you lot are just stood around," you say.
<<else>>
	"Why aren't you putting out the fire?" you ask.
<</if>>
<br><br>
<<generate1>><<person1>>
"Too dangerous," a <<person>> dressed as a firefighters says. "The building's made of, er, exotic materials, and we've confirmed there's no one inside. We're keeping an eye on it to make sure it doesn't spread elsewhere. That's the important thing. Been good so far. Suspiciously good, if you ask me."
