:: Mansion Robin
<<effects>><<wearProp "manila envelope">>

On the other side of the gate, staring up at the mansion in awe, is Robin.
<br><br>

<<He>> tears <<his>> gaze away as you approach, and smiles at you. "I didn't expect it to be so," <<He>> pauses. "Big." <<He>> reaches into <<his>> bag, produces a folder, and pushes it through the bars.
<br><br>

"Just a small gift from everyone," Robin says as you open it. It's full of letters, some long, some short, all thanking you, and wishing you the best. Some are illustrated with drawings of various complexity. There are many, some are even from ex-residents, much older than you.<<gstress>><<stress 6>><<ltrauma>><<trauma -6>>
<br><br>

<<link [["Thank Robin, and invite " + $NPCList[0].pronouns.him + " in"|Mansion Robin Invite]]>><</link>>
