:: Mansion Folder
<<effects>><<wearProp "paper sheet">>

You sit on the bed and flip through the folder, stopping to read the letters as takes your fancy. You don't remember all the events portrayed, but you don't doubt they're true.
<br><br>

<<if $avery_mansion.folder gte 3 and $saved_orphanage_picture is undefined>>
	Something half-slips out from in between the letters. Something you didn't see before. <span class="blue">It's a small laminated photo.</span>
	<br><br>

	You feel strange as your thumb rubs across it. It's you and Robin when you were younger. Next to the two of you is Bailey, facing the camera with an uninterested expression.
	<<nnpc_His "Bailey">> eyes are trained on someone standing behind you and Robin, who rests a hand on each of your shoulders.
	<br><br>

	You pull the photo free to get a better look. The person behind you is dressed casually. The upper half of their face is blurred and marred, leaving them unrecognisable. You can see their smile, though.
