<<else>>
	"It wasn't yours to throw away," you say.
<</if>>
<br><br>

Avery shrugs. "I thought you were done with it. You've looked at it enough. Besides, the sooner you forget about that vulgar place, the better."
<br><br>

Avery emerges from the wardrobe, a fresh pair of shoes in hand, and walks away.
<br><br>

<<if $saved_orphanage_picture>>
