:: Mansion Fox Heist Vault Whip 4
<<effects>><<summon_brown_fox 1>><<person1>>

You wait, bound to the rack, left to your thoughts and the pain in your back.
<br><br>

You hear someone coming back down the stairs. You tense up. <<say_brown_fox "cap">> doesn't usually make that much noise.
<br><br>

Your worries vanish upon hearing <<his>> voice, though. "Sorry for making you wait. I've made sure Avery won't remember this, although <<nnpc_he "Avery">> might remember being angry."
<<He>> steps around you, caressing your cheek. "That all looked painful. Hold still." As if you could move if you wanted to.
<br><br>

<<He>> pulls something from another satchel under <<his>> cloak. You hear a short click, and feel something cool get poured over your back. A pair of gentle hands begin to rub it in.
It stings briefly, but a soothing chill spreads immediately after. <<pain -50>><<lllpain>>
<br><br>

You sigh in relief. <<He>> giggles. "Here, I know a few tricks." <<He>> begins pressing <<his>> thumbs into your back. <<He>> moves them in small circles, expertly finding every tense spot and forcing it to loosen.
You nearly moan at <<his>> touch, but manage to hold it in. <<stress -6>><<lstress>>
<br><br>

<<He>> starts to unbind you before you can get too comfortable. "Thank you for trusting me." <<He>> helps you stand, and returns to the keypad.
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Mansion Fox Heist Vault 2]]>><</link>>
<br>

