:: Mansion Fox Heist Vault 2
<<effects>>

It lets out a few more dull beeps, before they give way to a higher-pitched one. <span class="green">The vault door opens.</span> A purple smoke billows out, filling your lungs with an intense sweetness.<<garousal>><<arousal 600>>
<br><br>

You enter the vault with <<him>>, surrounded by metal walls, floor, and ceiling. It's empty save a purple cushion on a plinth.
<br><br>

Resting on the cushion, <span class="pink">a white so pale.</span> The wishing stones.
<br><br>

<<His>> hand moves, as if to reach for them, but <<he>> stops <<himself>>. "You're the reason we've come this far. It should be you who becomes their new keeper." <<He>> gestures forward.
<br><br>

You take the wishing stones. An energy rushes through your arm. For a moment, your vision is filled with a pale light, and a sensation of floating, as if underwater. <span class="green">You feel stronger.</span>
<br><br>

You leave the fake stones in their place. The two of you exit the vault. It seals shut behind you with a hiss.
<br><br>

<<set $auriga_artefact to "pc">><<set $fake_artefact to "Avery">>
