<<He>> lets out a deep breath. "We did it."
<<He>> stares down at the stones in your hand. After a moment, <<he>> grows a wide smile. "You've done a very good thing. The plan is set, and their ritual will backfire.
With the right subterfuge, we can <span class="green">speed up the construction of the tower</span>, and get this whole ordeal over with sooner."
