:: Mansion Piano Demon 2
<<effects>>
<<if $phase is 1>>
	You drop to your knees. Its sharp fingers follow you down.
	<<if $demon gte 6>>
		You feel small. Your horns feel like nubs compared to its glorious crown of antlers. <span class="red">This is something beyond a demon.</span>
	<<elseif $fallenangel gte 2>>
		You feel hollow, staring at an empty reflection of something so familiar. Like a cracked mirror.
	<<elseif $angel gte 6>>
		You feel humbled, brought low by something that is in every way your opposite.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	From the right side of its darkened face, a single green eye stares. It becomes more gentle, half-closing. Its hand gently grasps your shoulder, and pulls up. The command is clear. <span class="blue">Stand.</span>
	<br><br>

	You obey.
<<elseif $phase is 2>>
	You open your mouth, but no noise comes out. It understands, though.
	<br><br>

	Its head tilts curiously. From the right side of its darkened face, a single green eye stares. It becomes more gentle, half-closing.
<<elseif $phase is 3>>
	You open your mouth to scream, <span class="red">and only a faint mist escapes.</span> It flows forward, snaking around its fingers.
	<br><br>

	Its head tilts curiously. From the right side of its darkened face, a single green eye stares. It becomes more gentle, half-closing.
<<else>>
	<<if $willpowerSuccess>>
		You control your breathing, <span class="green">and stay calm.</span> The creature pauses, a single green eye staring at you from the right side of its darkened face. You feel an odd sensation, like something crawling over your scalp, then nothing.
	<<else>>
		You try to stay calm, but the aberration is too grotesque. <span class="red">It shouldn't be.</span>
		<br><br>
		You open your mouth to scream, <span class="red">and only a faint mist escapes.</span> It flows forward, snaking around its fingers.
		<br><br>

		Its head tilts curiously. From the right side of its darkened face, a single green eye stares. It becomes more gentle, half-closing.
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

You hear the straining and stretching of sinew as its arm moves. It places its hand flat against your chest. <span class="purple">Your heartbeat grows louder.</span>
<br><br>

<<if $gwylanSeen?.includes("ritual_sex")>>
	Its hand then moves, gently grabbing your arm. Its sharp fingers scratch you as it pulls you into an embrace. Despite everything else, it's warm. Comforting.
	Its eye closes, and you hear something like a sigh of relief as it feels your heart beating. You feel something leaving you. Its eye opens and it quickly withdraws from you as it realises this. <<purity -15>><<llpurity>>
	<br><br>
<<else>>
	<<if $avery_mansion.fox.progress gte 5 or $brownFoxRevealed>>
		Its eye closes, and you hear something like a sigh of relief as it feels your heart. Its hand retracts back into the shadows.
	<<else>>
		Its eye closes, satisfied by what it felt, and its hand retracts back into the shadows.
	<</if>>
<</if>>
It turns away and walks towards the mask on the floor, exposing itself fully to the moon. Its skin shines, marked by countless old scars. All is dead silent.
<br><br>

It puts the mask on. Its head twitches.
<br><br>

Something that was once a person turns around. Its hand slowly points to you, then back to itself. Black sludge trickles from its eyes down the cheeks of its mask.
No words are shared, but you understand. There is no glory, no pleasure here. This is damnation.
<br><br>

It's a warning. This is the path you're treading.
<br><br>

It lumbers back into the shadows, away from the cruel light. It raises its hand to you and closes it. Your eyes close on their own.
<br><br>

When they open again, <<he>> is gone. Nobody is here.
<br><br>

