		<<He>> lets out a dry, sad laugh. "<<nnpc_Hes "Harper">> still one step ahead of everyone else."
		<br><br>

		<<He>> sits back down.
		<<if $avery_mansion.fox.friend>>
			"I had come to the mansion to watch the tower with you. Congratulate you on a job well done, and share a drink.
		<<else>>
			"I had come to the mansion to look for you.
		<</if>>
		When I didn't find you here, I ran to the tower as fast as I could.
		<<if $avery_mansion.fox.saved>>
			I'm glad I made it to you in time."
		<<elseif $avery_fate is "saved">>
			You didn't need my help, though." <<He>> leans forward into the light just enough for you to see <<his>> smile. "Your flight was beautiful, dear."
		<<else>>
			I feared the worst."
		<</if>>
		<<if $avery_mansion.fox.friend>>
			<<set $mansion_fox_followup.pushUnique("can_drink")>>
			<br><br>
			You hear something slide against the top of the piano.
			<<if playerIsPregnant() and npcIsPregnant("Gwylan")>>
				Moonlight reflects off of two wine glasses, and a bottle of sparkling grape juice. "I keep my promises."
			<<elseif playerIsPregnant() or npcIsPregnant("Gwylan")>>
				Moonlight reflects off of two wine glasses, a bottle of wine, and a bottle of sparkling grape juice. "I keep my promises."
			<<else>>
				Moonlight reflects off of two wine glasses, and a bottle of wine. "I keep my promises."
			<</if>>
		<</if>>

		<<if $mansion_fox_followup.includes("reveal")>>
			<br><br>

			<<He>> looks away. "I'm also sorry for not telling you who I was sooner.
			<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_sex")>>
				It's not that I didn't trust you. It was just safer for you that way."
			<<else>>
				I had to make sure I could trust you with something this serious. Besides, it was safer for you this way."
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<<case "apologyAccept">>
		<<He>> smiles and bows. "Your heart is a kind one."
	<<case "apologyDeny">>
		<<He>> frowns and nods. "As is your right. I failed in my part, and it cost you dearly. I only hope that, one day, you'll find it in your heart to forgive me."
	<<case "drink">>
		<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("mask") and !$brownFoxRevealed>>
			<<set $mansion_fox_followup.pushUnique("mask")>>
			<<He>> dons <<his>> mask and steps into the light.
		<</if>>
		<<He>> pours your drinks.
		<<if $avery_fate is "saved">>
			The two of you cheer, your glasses clinking together just a little louder than you had intended. You both wince, looking up the stairs towards the bedroom. No noise comes from it. <<say_brown_fox "Gwylan">> giggles, and you drink.
		<<else>>
			The two of you cheer, your glasses clinking together. You drink.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<He>> lets out a satisfied huff after downing <<his>> glass. "It tastes so much better with a partner, doesn't it?" <<if $brownFoxRevealed>><<gyearning>><<else>><<note "+ ???" "forest-green">><</if>>
		<<if $gwylanSeen>>
			<<npcincr Gwylan dom 2>>
			<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("bf_drink")>>
		<</if>>
	<<case "bonesReal">>
		<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("bonesFake")>>
			"I suppose I owe you answers. I don't normally speak so freely." <<He>> paces.
		<</if>>
		"They're wrist bones. That's why they're called 'clutching bones.' They're very old. Preserved as a holy relic. Or an unholy one, depending on who you ask."
		<br><br>

		<<He>> turns to you. "Hold on to them. You're their keeper, now."
	<<case "bonesFake">>
		<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("bonesReal")>>
			"I suppose I owe you answers. I don't normally speak so freely." <<He>> paces.
		<</if>>
		"They were the bones of a deceased whale, picked clean. It gave life to those at the bottom. It takes life back from those at the top just as easily."
		<br><br>

		<<He>> folds <<his>> hands in front of <<him>>. "I hollowed them out, and carved them into shape from photos that Landry had of the real ones. The rest was simple chemistry." <<His>> explanation is cold and clinical, lacking any sort of pride or emotion.
	<<case "thank">>
		<<He>> looks away. "It was my fault you were in that position to begin with. I don't deserve your thanks.
		<<if $avery_fate is "saved">>
			You alone saved Avery. No one else could have." <<He>> pauses. "And I don't think anyone else would have, if given the same choice. You are so... so very curious."
		<<else>>
			You saved yourself."
		<</if>>
	<<case "thank_how">>
		"I'm not sure what you mean. All I did was push you out of the way, and help you out of the debris."
	<<case "thank_saw">>
		<<He>> doesn't respond.
	<<case "AveryMad">>
		<<He>> looks down. "I'm sorry. The High Elk was the primary target, or so I thought. We inflicted a wound, but the outcome was... not as intended."
		<<He>> looks up to the moon. "Our conflict has only just begun. I hope you stay clear of it. You've done so much already. More than you know."
	<<case "Avery">>
		<<He>> looks down. "I did. The High Elk was the primary target, or so I thought."
		<br><br>
		<<if $avery_fate is "saved">>
			<<He>> lets out a long breath. "Perhaps, someday, redemption will find Avery." <<He>> looks up to the moon. "Our conflict has only just begun.
		<<else>>
			<<He>> lets out a long breath. "In a way, Avery is saved. Saved from something worse. What happened was a mercy. Weep not for the fallen." <<He>> looks up to the moon. "Our conflict has only just begun. Mourning must wait until the end.
		<</if>>
		I hope you stay clear of it. You've done so much already. More than you know."
	<<case "help">>
		<<He>> doesn't respond at first, only looking down and covering <<his>> mouth.
		<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("mask") and !$brownFoxRevealed>>
			<<set $mansion_fox_followup.pushUnique("mask")>>
			<<He>> dons <<his>> mask and steps into the light.
		<<else>>
			<<He>> steps into the light.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		"Oh, my dear child." <<He>> hugs you.
		<<if $brownFoxRevealed>>
			"You've already helped me with so much. If you're certain..." <<He>> pulls away after a moment, smiling.
			"There's much work to be done, and I can't think of anyone else I'd rather have by my side." <<npcincr Gwylan dom 5>><<ggyearning>>
		<<else>>
			"You must have had a hard life, to give of yourself so willingly." <<He>> pulls back, smiling.
			"I'm still not used to working with others, but perhaps I've worked alone for too long. <span class="green">Some day soon, we will again.</span> I promise."
		<</if>>
	<<case "mask">>
		You try to get a closer look at <<his>> face. Every time you do, it seems as though a cloud blocks the light of the moon just enough to obscure it.
		<br><br>

		"You're just going to give yourself eye strain doing that, dear." <<He>> dons <<his>> mask.
	<<case "piano">>
		<<if $brownFoxRevealed and $seabird_lullaby gte 2>>
			<<He>> smiles. "I knew you would recognise my song. Isn't the melody soothing?"
		<<else>>
			"You know the melody, don't you?" <<He>> smiles. "Perhaps I'll share the words with you, some day."
		<</if>>
	<<case "flirt">>
		<<if $brownFoxRevealed and $gwylanSeen?.includes("ritual_sex")>>
			<<set $seductiondifficulty to (10000 - ((C.npc.Gwylan.lust * 50) + (C.npc.Gwylan.dom * 50)))>>
			<<seductioncheck>>
			<<seductionskilluptext>>
			<<seductionskilluse>>
			<<promiscuity1>>

			<<if $seductionrating gte $seductionrequired>>
				<<He>> giggles and blushes.
				<<if $avery_fate isnot "saved">>
					"Oh, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>, you want to indulge here of all places? Why not? In fact, I think that pile of charcoal over there was Avery's bed. Do you think it's still comfortable? How about you go lay down and test it for me?"
				<<else>>
					"Oh, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>, I don't think Avery would like you fooling around with someone like me right under <<nnpc_his "Avery">> nose. What if <<nnpc_he "Avery">> heard?"
				<</if>>
				<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("bf_flirt")>>
				<br><br>

				<<He>> steps forward and puts a finger under your chin, and uses <<his>> other hand to pat your head.
				"Save it for the ritual. We can have some fun then, alright? You've gotten me worked up now, so you best be ready for it." <<npcincr Gwylan lust 25>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 2>><<ggglust>><<gyearning>>
			<<else>>
				<<He>> giggles. "I appreciate the attempt, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>, but there's a time and a place for such courtship." <<He>> hesitates. "Maybe I'll help you temper your seductive abilities some time."
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<set $seductiondifficulty to 10000>>
			<<seductioncheck>>
			<<seductionskilluptext>>
			<<seductionskilluse>>
			<<promiscuity1>>

			<<if $seductionrating gte $seductionrequired>>
				<<He>> giggles.
				<<if $avery_fate is "saved">>
					"I don't think Avery would like that very much."
					<<He>> leans in. "Perhaps I'll sneak in some day while <<nnpc_hes "Avery">> away." <<He>> places a finger under your chin. "Or maybe you should keep such thoughts to yourself." <<He>> smiles sweetly. <<gglust>>
				<<else>>
					"I suppose you're open now that Avery's gone, aren't you?"
					<<He>> leans in. "Perhaps I'll come find you sooner than anticipated, for pleasure before business." <<He>> places a finger under your chin. "Or maybe you should keep such thoughts to yourself." <<He>> smiles sweetly. <<gglust>>
				<</if>>
				<<if $gwylanSeen>>
					<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("bf_flirt")>>
				<</if>>
			<<else>>
				<<He>> giggles. "I'm flattered, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>, but I'm far too much for you."
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<<case "leave">>
		<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("mask")>>
			<<set $mansion_fox_followup.pushUnique("mask")>>
			<<He>> dons <<his>> mask.
		<</if>>
		"How rude, not even saying hello."
		<br><br>

		<<He>> kicks off of the piano and lands right in front of you, <<his>> face still obscured by shadows. <<He>> places a finger under your chin. "Be a good <<girl>> and smell the roses, won't you?"
		<br><br>

		You try to move around <<him>>, but <<he>> keeps leaning in your way. You don't have much choice but to stay, for now.
	<<default>><<He>> sneezes cutely.
<</switch>>
<<set $mansion_fox_followup.pushUnique($mansion_fox_talk)>>
<br><br>

<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("apology")>>
	<<link [[Ask what <<hes>> sorry for|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "apology">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includesAny("apologyAccept", "apologyDeny")>>
	<<link [[Accept apology|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "apologyAccept">><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Deny apology|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "apologyDeny">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if $mansion_fox_followup.includes("apology") and !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("bonesReal") and !$avery_mansion.fox.bones>>
	<<link [[Ask what the wishing stones really are|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "bonesReal">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if $mansion_fox_followup.includes("apology") and !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("bonesFake") and !$avery_mansion.fox.bones>>
	<<link [[Ask what the fake stones really were|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "bonesFake">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if $mansion_fox_followup.includes("can_drink") and !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("drink")>>
	<<if playerIsPregnant()>>
		<<link [[Drink with <<him>>|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "drink">><</link>>
		<br>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[Drink with <<him>>|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "drink">><<alcohol 60>><</link>><<galcohol>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<<if $avery_mansion.fox.saved>>
	<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("thank")>>
		<<if $avery_fate is "saved">>
			<<link [[Thank <<him>> for saving you and Avery|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "thank">><</link>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[Thank <<him>> for saving you|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "thank">><</link>>
			<br>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif $mansion_fox_followup.includes("thank") and !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("thank_how")>>
		<<link [[Ask how <<he>> saved you|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "thank_how">><</link>>
		<br>
	<<elseif $mansion_fox_followup.includes("thank_how") and !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("thank_saw")>>
		<<link [[Say you never saw <<him>> escape|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "thank_saw">><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includesAny("Avery", "AveryMad")>>
	<<if $avery_fate is "saved">>
		<<link [[Get angry about <<his>> idea of 'saving' Avery|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "AveryMad">><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[Say you thought <<he>> wanted to save Avery|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "Avery">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if $mansion_fox_followup.includesAny("Avery", "AveryMad") and !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("help")>>
	<<link [[Say you'll help however you can|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "help">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("mask")>>
	<<link [[Try to get a better look at <<his>> face|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "mask">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("piano")>>
	<<link [[Ask <<him>> about the song <<he>> was playing|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "piano">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<<if $mansion_fox_followup.includes("drink") and !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("flirt")>>
	<<link [[Flirt|Mansion Piano Fox Talk]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "flirt">><</link>><<promiscuous1>>
	<br>
<</if>>
<br>

<<if $mansion_fox_followup.includesAny("apologyAccept", "apologyDeny")>>
	<<link [[Say goodbye to <<say_brown_fox>>|Mansion Piano Fox Talk End]]>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<if $avery_mansion.fox.friend or $mansion_fox_followup.includes("help") and !$brownFoxRevealed>>
		<<link [[Say goodbye, and that you hope to meet again soon|Mansion Piano Fox Talk End]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "soon">><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("help") and !$brownFoxRevealed>>
		<<link [[Say you hope you never have to meet each other again|Mansion Piano Fox Talk End]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "never">><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
<<elseif !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("leave") and !$brownFoxRevealed>>
	<<link [[Just leave|Mansion Piano Fox Talk End]]>><<set $mansion_fox_talk to "leave">><</link>>
	<br>
<</if>>

:: Mansion Piano Fox Talk End
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $mansion_fox_followup.includes("can_drink") and !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("drink")>>
	<<He>> frowns, sliding the wine and glasses back into the shadows.
<</if>>
<<if !$mansion_fox_followup.includes("mask") or $brownFoxRevealed>>
	<<He>> dons <<his>> mask.
<</if>>
<<if $brownFoxRevealed>>
	"I'll be at the shop. Come see me soon, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>."
<<else>>
	<<if $mansion_fox_talk is "soon">>
		"It may be sooner than you think.
	<<elseif $mansion_fox_talk is "never">>
		"I'm afraid I have no control over that, my dear.
	<<else>>
		"Until we meet again.
	<</if>>
	I'll be going dark for a time. May your triumphs and troubles shape you into diamond."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if $brownFoxRevealed and $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
	<<He>> starts to walk by you, but stops. <<He>> quickly pulls you into a kiss. <<gwylanKiss>>
	<br><br>

	"You're such a good <<girl>>. Thank you again for everything, my dear." With one last quick peck on the lips, <<he>> vanishes into the night. <<npcincr Gwylan dom 15>><<gggyearning>>
<<elseif $avery_mansion.fox.progress gte 15 and $mansion_fox_talk isnot "never" and $mansion_fox_followup.includes("drink")>>
	<<He>> starts to walk by you, but stops. <<He>> places a hand on your shoulder. "You are so very curious. I look forward to working together like this again." <<He>> vanishes into the night. <<npcincr Gwylan dom 5>><<if $brownFoxRevealed>><<ggyearning>><<else>><<note "+ + ???" "forest-green">><</if>>
<<else>>
	<<He>> brushes by you, and vanishes into the night. <<npcincr Gwylan dom 2>><<if $brownFoxRevealed>><<gyearning>><<else>><<note "+ ???" "forest-green">><</if>>
<</if>>
<<unset $mansion_fox_followup>><<unset $mansion_fox_talk>>
<<set $avery_mansion.fox.end to true>>
<<if $gwylan?.wary gte 1>>
	<<set $gwylan.wary to 0>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if $avery_fate isnot "saved">>
	<<link [[Next|Mansion Ruin]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
<<else>>
	<<link [[Next|Mansion Lounge]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
<</if>>
<br>


:: Mansion Leave
<<effects>>

You peer through the mansion gates. Seeing no one around, you step outside, and hurry down the path along the side of the road. You stop whenever a car approaches the bend up ahead, and stay still behind one of the spruces.
<br><br>

<<if Time.dayState is "night">>
	You see no other pedestrians, and make it to Danube Street unmolested.
<<else>>
	More than once, you're forced to take the side paths to hide from pedestrians, but you make it to Danube Street unmolested.
<</if>>

<<if $daily.ex.mansion isnot 1>>
	<<set $daily.ex.mansion to 1>>
	<<if $exposed gte 2>>
		<<if Time.dayState is "night">>
			<<exhibitionism4>>
		<<else>>
			<<exhibitionism5>>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<if Time.dayState is "night">>
			<<exhibitionism2>>
		<<else>>
			<<exhibitionism3>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<br><br>
<</if>>

<<if $avery_mansion.fox.known and $brownFoxWoundedTimer and !$brownFoxWounded and !isGwylanAbsent()>>
	<<link [[Next|Mansion Brown Fox Wounded]]>><</link>>
<<else>>
	<<link [[Next|Danube Street]]>><</link>>
<</if>>
<br>

:: Mansion Talk Ask Apologise
<<effects>>

<<if $speech_attitude is "meek" or $speech_attitude_avery>>
	"I-I'm sorry for turning you down, Avery," you mumble, looking at the <<= [outside] ? "ground" : "floor">>.
	<br><br>
<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
	You sigh. "I'm sorry, Avery," you say with only a hint of irony in your tone.
	<br><br>
<<else>>
	"I'm sorry, Avery," you say. "Things have just been hectic for me lately."
	<br><br>
<</if>>

Avery scrutinises you for a long moment, as though <<he>> were trying to measure how genuine your apology is. Regardless of <<his>> conclusion, <<he>>
<<if $averyragerevealed is 1 and C.npc.Avery.rage gte 60>>
	nods imperiously.
<<elseif $averyragerevealed is 1 and C.npc.Avery.rage gte 20>>
	smiles with satisfaction.
<<else>>
	smiles.
<</if>>
<br><br>
"Very well. <<= $averyragerevealed gte 1 ? "You're lucky that" : "Luckily,">> I've been too busy to cancel the reservations, so we still have our table. I'll see you on Valentine's Day, at our usual time."
<br><br>
<i>Avery will expect you to meet <<him>> at <<ampm 21 00>> on February 14th.</i>
<br><br>

<<endevent>>
<<avery_mansion_end_links>>


:: Mansion Talk Ask Apologise Refuse
<<effects>>

"Well," Avery says. "I could hardly take you to the most exclusive restaurant in town without an apology. It wouldn't be proper. Let me know if you change your mind."
<br><br>

<<endevent>>
<<avery_mansion_end_links>>
